content: In an underground lab located somewhere in the frigid tundra of Alaska, an unnamed and highly intoxicated scientist is on a quest to genetically engineer the Gooney Toons. For what is the purpose of creating 2-meter tall upright walking beasts? Some say this is a twisted nostalgia trip fuelled by too much LSD. Or maybe it’s that some men just want to see the world burn… at the hands of cartoon animals.
title: Birth of Goonies
